### Payment Methods API Testing
### Base URL: https://localhost:7001/api/cms/payment-methods

### 1. Get All Payment Methods (with pagination and filtering)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/cms/payment-methods?page=1&pageSize=10&search=VnPay&isOnlinePayment=true&sortBy=name&isAscending=true
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### 2. Get Payment Method by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/cms/payment-methods/123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### 3. Create Payment Method
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/cms/payment-methods
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data

{
    "name": "VnPay",
    "description": "Vietnam Payment Gateway",
    "iconImage": [file],
    "isOnlinePayment": true,
    "processingFee": 2.5,
    "processorName": "VnPay",
    "configuration": "{\"merchantId\":\"123\",\"secretKey\":\"abc\"}",
    "status": 1
}

### 4. Update Payment Method
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/cms/payment-methods/123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data

{
    "name": "VnPay Updated",
    "description": "Updated Vietnam Payment Gateway",
    "iconImage": [file],
    "isOnlinePayment": true,
    "processingFee": 3.0,
    "processorName": "VnPay",
    "configuration": "{\"merchantId\":\"456\",\"secretKey\":\"def\"}",
    "status": 1
}

### 5. Delete Payment Method
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/cms/payment-methods/123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Sample Filter Parameters:
# Basic pagination
?page=1&pageSize=10

# Search by name/description/processor
?search=VnPay

# Filter by payment type
?isOnlinePayment=true
?isOnlinePayment=false

# Filter by fee range
?minProcessingFee=1.0&maxProcessingFee=5.0

# Sorting options
?sortBy=name&isAscending=true
?sortBy=processingFee&isAscending=false
?sortBy=createdat&isAscending=false

# Combined filters
?page=1&pageSize=20&search=Pay&isOnlinePayment=true&minProcessingFee=1.0&sortBy=name&isAscending=true

